[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 3.0,
    "text": "Are you sure we should be doing this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "Maybe we could try talking to the other kids and..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "Or we could just drink the formula and see what happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "Cheers!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "I'm old!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "We're all old!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "Maybe the professor won't notice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Of course I noticed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "And I'm very disappointed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "You're disappointed?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "My teeth won't even stay in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "Speak up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "I can't hear you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "Who are you people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Professor, you gotta make us young again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "I'll work on an antidote while you're at school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "School?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "You don't want to ruin your perfect attendance on the second day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Well, now that we're old, at least we'll get some respect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "I take it back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "This is officially the worst."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "Whatcha gettin'?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 75.0,
    "text": "Booties for your grandkids?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "No, it's a caboodle for your noodle, my child."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Sounds sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Us next!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 88.0,
    "text": "Give us your lunch money, old lady!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "I don't have any money, but I have some hard candy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "We don't want hard candy, Grandma!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "I understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "This candy is probably too hard for you anyways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "What are you saying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Big Joey here can't handle your little bit of candy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "Hey, this ain't totally terrible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "Grab some more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "Us too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "And that is how Christopher Columbus discovered America."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Christopher Columbus didn't discover America."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "It was the Vikings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "I said no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "I was on Leif Erikson's boat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "So that's how he defeated Dracula and the shark people and discovered Salt Lake City."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "I think I may have figured out the antidote."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "Or maybe not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Thank you for the hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "Thank you for the hard candy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Great stories, Granny Buttercup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "Tomorrow I'll tell you about the battle with the Plutonians."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "Darn these dentures!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Here, Grandma Buttercup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 168.0,
    "text": "I also got you some denture cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "Same as my Nana."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "Stronger than mega glue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "Thanks, Sport."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "Who knew being super old would get us so much treat cred?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "Still, what I wouldn't give to have one more stab at youth again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "Nothing, Mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Just walking the dog."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 193.0,
    "text": "Or should I say, he is walking Mojo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "What's that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "Yeah, of course I'm getting you a birthday present."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 202.0,
    "text": "Powerpuff Girls!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Mojo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "You are wrinkly old ladies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "Are you sure that's Mojo?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.0,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "Looks like a cactus or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "Yes, it is Mojo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "Oh, the hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "The evil laugh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "The winning smile."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "Hi, Mojo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "You're so old and wrinkly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 224.0,
    "text": "You will never again interfere with my genius master plans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "We might be old, but we still got Pep in our step."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 233.0,
    "text": "Come on, girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "Let's get him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.0,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "Mojo grows tired of this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "He would love to stay, but he has important crimes to commit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "And personal errands to run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "You stay here, buddy, and watch those grannies until I return."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.0,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "With money and stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.0,
    "endTime": 280.0,
    "text": " You"
  }
]